cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the evaluation of systems that process Knowledge Graphs, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the use of benchmarks is a common practice in the field of systems and information (cs.SI).
